CS184 Assignment 5

PARTNERS:
------------------
cs184-dv  Niels Joubert
cs184-ah  Hannah Hu

BUILDING:
-----------------
gmake 


RUNNING:
-----------------
./cs184_as5 inputfile.bez stepSize [-a] [-q] [-d n]

	-a		adaptive tessellation
	-q		no output (quiet)
	-d n	debug printout (n = level, 1 through 5)

KEYBOARD INPUTS:
----------------

left, right, up, down, <, >		- rotate object around 3 axis
	
[CTRL] + above					- give object momentum in direction

[SHIRT] + left,right,up,down	- translate object
	
-, +							- zoom camera in, out

n								- show normals

d								- show derivates


PLATFORM:
------------------
GNU/Linux - Should run on Solaris just fine.


Makefile concerns:
-------------------
This should be taken care of, but...
Be sure to include the GLUT libraries in the makefile:

	LIBS := -lglut -lGLU -lGL -lX11
	
	
	
